  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK863">
<l>añcu maṟiyā ṉamaivila ṉīkalāṉ </l>
<l>ṟañca meḷiyaṉ pakaikku</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>In the estimation of foes miserably weak is he, who is timid, ignorant, unsociable and niggardly.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
